query:
SELECT s.siteNumber, s.size, s.maxTables, c.name as centreName 
FROM sites s 
JOIN shopping_centres c ON s.centreId = c.id 
WHERE c.name LIKE '%Campbelltown%' 
ORDER BY s.siteNumber 
LIMIT 5
